  "texts": [
    "Students were instructed to generate a shareable link to their logs and submit it via the LMS.",
    "They were explicitly informed that their ChatGPT interactions would remain confidential, inaccessible to the course instructor, and would not influence their grades.",
    "In addition, students were notified about a post-session quiz to be completed without any external help, including ChatGPT.",
    "This quantitative data collection aimed to assess individual student comprehension and retention of the concepts covered during the sessions.",
    "The quizzes, administered online via the LMS, consisted of 18, 20, and 16 multiple-choice questions, respectively, for each of the three intervention sessions."
  ],
